		   README for LTMP (Lighttpd Mysql PHP)

INFOMATION
-------------------------
Why do you recreate the weel called the LTMP?
Smaller, faster, more efficently.   


INSTALL
------------------------- 
gunzip -cd ltmp.tar.gz | tar xvf -
cd ltmp
./ltmp.sh <domain> <mysql_password>


